INSTALLATION
============

1. Install django-tastypie as directed

https://django-tastypie.readthedocs.org/en/latest/tutorial.html#installation

2. Install tastypie-optimizers using pip or easy_install.

$ pip install tastypie-optimizers

3. Temporarily, add "tastypie_optimizers" to INSTALLED_APPS.

This lets you try the sample application & run the unittest suite.

Run Unit Tests
==============

Run the unittest suite to prove this works with your version of tastypie.

$ python manage.py test tastypie_optimizers.tests

